"Sampled (default 1%) chunk-level lifecycle tracking via "
"``L1LifecycleSubscriber``. Only sampled chunks contribute to histograms; "
"counters above always count all events. Sampling is deterministic (hash-"
"based), so the same key always gets the same decision with zero memory "
"overhead."
